<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="vision-mission-hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Our Vision & Mission</h1>
                <p>Guiding principles that illuminate our path towards educational excellence and societal impact.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="vision-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Vision: A Future Transformed by Education</h2>
                <p>Nageshwaram Foundation Trust envisions a vibrant and equitable society where every individual, particularly from rural backgrounds, has access to empowering educational opportunities. We aspire to create a generation of confident, skilled, and ethically conscious citizens who are capable of driving positive change in their communities and the nation. Our vision is to be a catalyst for socio-economic upliftment through education, fostering innovation, critical thinking, and a deep sense of responsibility towards humanity and the environment.</p>
                <p>We see our institutions as centers of excellence, not just in academics but in holistic development, where traditional values blend seamlessly with modern pedagogical approaches. We aim to inspire a lifelong love for learning, preparing students not just for careers, but for meaningful lives.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mission-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Mission: Nurturing Minds, Building Character</h2>
                <p>To realize our vision, Nageshwaram Foundation Trust is committed to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>**Providing Quality Education:** Establishing and supporting educational institutions that offer a comprehensive, balanced, and relevant curriculum from foundational learning to advanced studies.</li>
                    <li>**Fostering Holistic Development:** Implementing programs that enhance intellectual, physical, emotional, and spiritual well-being, encouraging creativity, leadership, and resilience.</li>
                    <li>**Promoting Inclusivity:** Ensuring equitable access to education for all children, especially those from marginalized sections of society, through affordable and supportive learning environments.</li>
                    <li>**Empowering Educators:** Recruiting, training, and continuously developing dedicated teachers who are passionate about nurturing young minds and fostering a positive learning atmosphere.</li>
                    <li>**Engaging Communities:** Building strong partnerships with parents, local authorities, and community leaders to create a collaborative ecosystem that supports student success and community welfare.</li>
                    <li>**Encouraging Innovation:** Embracing modern teaching methodologies, technology, and research to keep our educational offerings dynamic and effective.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Join Our Journey</h2>
                <p>Together, we can achieve our vision of a better tomorrow, shaped by enlightened minds and strong characters.</p>
                <a href="/institutions" class="cta-button primary">Explore Our Institutions</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
